name: Core
description: Core is a community-driven token born from the viral Corecore meme movement. It’s a cultural signal—spreading the message and aesthetic that Core is all about. Core has always been here, quietly woven into the fabric of internet culture, and now people are starting to remember. Its mission is to reach and connect people across TikTok, X, and other platforms who resonate with the raw, thought-provoking, and emotionally charged Corecore vibe. By blending nostalgia, creativity, and decentralized coordination, Core Token turns shared memory into a growing movement.
